<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mellen Oliveira | Premium Mentoring & Safety</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@200;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #050505;
            --accent: #D4AF37; /* Dourado Clássico */
            --accent-light: #F9E4B7;
            --text-muted: #a0a0a0;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Efeito de Gradiente de Fundo */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        header {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, var(--accent), #fff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 200;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* --- BUTTONS --- */
        .btn-gold {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-gold:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* --- SECTIONS --- */
        section {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: "";
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--accent);
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        /* --- EXPERIENCE GRID --- */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--glass);
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            transition: 0.3s;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.02);
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* --- SPECIFIC AREAS --- */
        .dual-service {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .service-box {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .contact-link {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .dual-service { flex-direction: column; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/seu-usuario/seu-repo/main/profile.png" alt="Mellen Oliveira" class="profile-img">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Mellen Oliveira</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">High-Level Communication & Safety</p>
        <a href="#english" class="btn-gold">SOLICITAR AULAS PARTICULARES</a>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <section id="english">
            <h2 class="section-title">English Mentoring</h2>
            <div class="dual-service">
                <div class="service-box">
                    <h3>Vivência Internacional</h3>
                    <p>Com quase 10 anos de experiência acumulada na <b>Bélgica e Holanda</b>, desenvolvi uma fluência que transcende o acadêmico. Minha abordagem é focada na comunicação real, adaptabilidade cultural e no refinamento linguístico necessário para ambientes multiculturais de alto nível.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 30px; font-style: italic; color: var(--text-muted);">
                        "Mais do que ensinar um idioma, eu conecto você ao mundo através de uma comunicação excepcional."
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://forms.gle/seu-link-aqui" target="_blank" class="btn-gold">RESERVAR MINHA VAGA</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);">

        <section id="safety">
            <h2 class="section-title">Safety & Operations</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Segurança do Trabalho</h3>
                    <p>Técnica pela ETEC, especializada em protocolos de segurança, NR-13 e primeiros socorros. Foco absoluto na preservação do capital humano e conformidade técnica.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Gestão de Operações</h3>
                    <p>Experiência robusta na Cronos Engenharia, gerenciando logística complexa, agendas de engenharia e atendimento corporativo de alta demanda.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Coordenação Global</h3>
                    <p>Expertise em logística de viagens internacionais e recepção de clientes, garantindo que cada detalhe operacional seja executado com perfeição.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 60px; text-align: center;">
                <p>Para parcerias corporativas e consultoria técnica:</p>
                <a href="mailto:teachermellenoliveira@gmail.com" class="contact-link" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">teachermellenoliveira@gmail.com</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 MELLEN OLIVEIRA. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
        <p>Desenvolvido para mentes exclusivas.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
